            <title>[LUDOC-52] generated Html doc has broken internal references when they cross separate xml files.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-52</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve found a broken link in the generated HTML:&lt;/p&gt;

