&lt;p&gt;The broken link is in the section above and is: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;see Chapter 23: Testing Lustre Network Performance (LNET Self-Test).&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
